<!-- Diagnosis and symptoms -->
'''念珠菌性阴道炎'''（{{lang-en|Candidal vulvovaginitis}}），是一种常见的、由[[白色念珠菌|白色念珠菌]]引起的阴道炎症。念珠菌还可寄生在人的口腔、皮肤、阴道等，并可自身互相传染。念珠菌阴道炎的病原体为白色念珠菌，属真菌<ref name="Andrews">{{cite book |author=James, William D.; Berger, Timothy G.; et al. |title=Andrews' Diseases of the Skin: clinical Dermatology |url=https://archive.org/details/andrewsdiseasess00mdwi_659 |publisher=Saunders Elsevier |year=2006 |page=[https://archive.org/details/andrewsdiseasess00mdwi_659/page/309 309] |isbn=0-7216-2921-0 }}</ref>。常見症狀包括外阴、阴道极度瘙痒<!-- <ref name=WH2014/> -->，[[阴道分泌物|白带]]增多，多呈白色豆渣样或凝乳样。典型的白带为白色、凝乳块和豆腐渣样，膜附有白色膜状物。小阴唇内侧面及阴道膜红肿或糜烂，甚至有浅表溃疡。治疗的方式通常包括抗生素和抗霉药剂<ref name=Lancet2007>{{cite journal|last=Sobel|first=JD|title=Vulvovaginal candidosis.|journal=Lancet|date=9 June 2007 |volume=369|issue=9577|pages=1961–71|pmid=17560449|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(07)60917-9}}</ref>。严重时外阴疼痛难忍，坐卧不宁，可能導致[[排尿困難|排尿時有灼痛感]]、頻尿，以及性交疼痛。妇科检查可见外阴肿胀潮红<ref name=WH2014/>。症狀在經期時可能惡化<ref name=Lancet2007/>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
念珠菌性陰道炎是肇因於女性生殖道的[[假丝酵母属|念珠菌]]過度繁殖<!-- <ref name=WH2014/> -->。念珠菌本屬人體內的正常菌叢，但過度生長可以致病<ref name=WH2014/>。該病並不屬於[[性傳染病|性傳染病]]，但性交頻繁者會增加感染的機率<ref name=WH2014/><ref name=Lancet2007/>。風險因子包含服用[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]、[[妊娠|妊娠]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]，以及[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]<ref name=Lancet2007/>。高[[單醣|單醣]]飲食也可能提高感染機會<ref name=WH2014/>。而衣服過緊、內褲種類，以及個人衛生習慣則應該與此病關連不大<ref name=Lancet2007>{{cite journal|last=Sobel|first=JD|title=Vulvovaginal candidosis.|journal=Lancet|date=9 June 2007 |volume=369|issue=9577|pages=1961–71|pmid=17560449|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(07)60917-9}}</ref>。由於該病症狀類似性傳染病、[[披衣菌感染|披衣菌感染]]，以及淋病，因此建議進行陰道分泌物培養以利診斷<ref name=WH2014/>。

<!-- Treatment -->
雖然缺乏證據，但一般建議穿著棉質內褲及寬鬆衣物以預防感染<ref name=WH2014/><ref name=Lancet2007/>。另也建議避免使用{{tsl|en|douching||陰道盥洗}}及芳香衛生產品<ref name=WH2014/>。該病需以[[抗真菌药|抗真菌药]]治療<!-- <ref name=CDC2006/> -->，可在患部給予[[克催瑪汝|克催瑪汝]]軟膏及[[氟康唑|氟康唑]]等<ref name=CDC2006>{{cite journal |author=Workowski KA, Berman SM |title=Sexually transmitted diseases treatment guidelines, 2006 |journal=MMWR Recomm Rep |volume=55 |issue=RR-11 |pages=1–94 |date=August 2006 |pmid=16888612 |url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/rr5511a1.htm |access-date=2016-05-28 |archive-date=2019-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803065818/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/rr5511a1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而[[益生菌|益生菌]]則顯示對正在感染的患者沒有實質幫助<ref name=Abad2009>{{cite journal|last=Abad|first=CL|author2=Safdar, N|title=The role of lactobacillus probiotics in the treatment or prevention of urogenital infections – a systematic review.|journal=Journal of chemotherapy (Florence, Italy)|date=June 2009|volume=21|issue=3|pages=243–52|pmid=19567343|doi=10.1179/joc.2009.21.3.243}}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology -->
大約75%的女性在一生中至少曾經受過一次念珠菌感染，有近半數甚至感染兩次以上<ref name=WH2014>{{cite web|title=Vaginal yeast infections fact sheet|url=http://www.womenshealth.gov/publications/our-publications/fact-sheet/vaginal-yeast-infections.html?from=AtoZ|website=Office on Women's Health|accessdate=5 March 2015|date=December 23, 2014|archive-date=2015-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150304034823/http://www.womenshealth.gov/publications/our-publications/fact-sheet/vaginal-yeast-infections.html?from=AtoZ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Mari2000/>。約有 5% 甚至可能在一年內感染三次以上<ref name=Mari2000>{{cite journal |author=Egan ME, Lipsky MS |title=Diagnosis of vaginitis |journal=Am Fam Physician |volume=62 |issue=5 |pages=1095–104 |date=September 2000 |pmid=10997533 |url=http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000901/1095.html |access-date=2016-05-28 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606054114/http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000901/1095.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該病為仅次于[[细菌性阴道病|细菌性阴道病]]后的第二类最常见阴道炎<ref name=Epi2011>{{cite journal|last=Ilkit|first=M|author2=Guzel, AB|title=The epidemiology, pathogenesis, and diagnosis of vulvovaginal candidosis: a mycological perspective |journal=Critical reviews in microbiology|date=August 2011 |volume=37|issue=3|pages=250–61|pmid=21599498|doi=10.3109/1040841X.2011.576332}}</ref>。

